I"©<p>LioranBoard has some very useful premade triggers.   <br />
For example, you can make your buttons automatically trigger every time you start LioranBoard or every time your LioranBoard connects to Transmitter.</p>

<h5 id="attach-a-premade-trigger-to-a-button">Attach a premade trigger to a button</h5>
<p>You can attach a premade trigger by right clicking on a button - Add/Edit Twitch Triggers, clicking on the + sign and selecting Extension trigger.</p>

